      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, but I'm seeing a lot of irregular bubbling and small fissures in the starter when it peaks. Could you explain the enzymatic process happening with the starch and how that physical structure is formed? Is it just the CO2, or is there more to the breakdown of the flour itself?",
